criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Compensated type 2 diabetes mellitus or with adequate control based on the criteria of
             the Brazilian Society of Diabetes (SBD, 2012);

          2. Chronic periodontitis (AAP, 2001);

          3. Presence of at least 15 teeth and at least four teeth with bleeding upon probing and
             probing depth greater than 4 mm;

          4. Aged 18 years or older;

          5. Under follow up with an endocrinologist.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Uncompensated diabetes, based on SBD criteria;

          2. Smoking habit in 12 months prior to treatment;

          3. Anemia;

          4. Active cancer;

          5. Current pregnancy;

          6. History of antibiotic therapy in previous six months;

          7. History of anti-inflammatory therapy in previous three months;

          8. Clotting disorder (use of anti-coagulant, presence of liver disease, thrombocytopenia
             and immunosuppression);

          9. Currently undergoing orthodontic treatment.
